snippet.title: Kirby's Dream Land 2 - Full Game - 100% Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Enjoy my Gameplay of Kirby's Dream Land 2 - Complete Game Walkthrough 100%.

►Timecodes:

00:00:00 Level 1 - Grass Land (Boss: Whispy Woods)
00:07:41 Level 2 - Big Forest (Boss: Nruff)
00:15:31 Level 3 - Ripple Field (Boss: Sweet Stuff)
00:25:29 Level 4 - Iceberg (Boss: Ice Dragon)
00:37:04 Level 5 - Red Canyon (Boss: Mr. Shine & Mr. Bright)
00:50:21 Level 6 - Cloudy Park (Boss: Kracko)
01:07:21 Level 7 - Dark Castle (Boss: King Dedede)
01:20:50 Final Boss: Dark Matter (first form + true form)

►Game Informations:
▪Developer: HAL Laboratory
▪Publisher: Nintendo
▪Director: Shinichi Shimonura
▪Producers: Satoru Iwata, Shigeru Miyamoto
▪Composer: Hirokazu Ando, Tadashi Ikegami
▪Series: Kirby
▪Platform: Game Boy
▪Release dates: 
-JP March 21, 1995
-NA May 1, 1995
-EU July 31, 1995
▪Genre: Platform game
▪Modes: Single player
▪Playtime: 3+ hours
